      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FREDDY LIVE WIRE (7) scored by 2.25 lengths last time (21.58) in a Grade 5 over 375m at this track. Expected to be in the finish. STATE OF MADNESS (1) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 5.5 lengths at this track in a handy 21.82 beating Rivia Thea. Unbeaten from this box in two starts. Form should stack up. SKEDADDLE PERCY (4) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a third place finish (31.27) there the start prior. Has a good record here at this journey. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. SIMPKIN (5) was in the money last start and poses a threat again.",
